      "parameters": {
        "content": "## #5 Telegram 通知測試\n\n**目的**：最快驗證 setup-wizard 建的 Telegram bot credential 真的能用。\n\n**測試方法**：\n1. 點 Execute workflow\n2. 你的 Telegram 應該立刻收到訊息「✅ Lite Pack 通知測試成功！...」\n3. 沒收到？看錯誤訊息，回 setup-wizard 重設 Telegram credential\n\n**改造方向**：\n- 把這個 workflow 當「通知 sub-workflow」，其他 workflow 用 Execute Workflow 節點呼叫\n- 加變數讓呼叫端可傳「emoji」「主標」「內文」自訂訊息\n- 加圖片附件（用 sendPhoto 取代 sendMessage）",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 360
      },
      "id": "sticky-05",
      "name": "📌 使用說明",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -260,
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "id": "trigger-05",
      "name": "Manual Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        240,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "msg-05",
